### Trancendos Platform — REST Client quick-tests
### Use with VS Code "REST Client" extension (humao.rest-client)
### Switch environment: Ctrl+Shift+P → "Rest Client: Switch Environment" → local

@spark     = {{spark_url}}
@grid      = {{grid_url}}
@auth      = {{auth_url}}
@langchain = {{langchain_url}}
@llamaindex = {{llamaindex_url}}
@haystack  = {{haystack_url}}
@dspy      = {{dspy_url}}


# ── Core health checks ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Backend health
GET {{spark}}/health

### The Digital Grid health
GET {{grid}}/health

### Infinity auth health
GET {{auth}}/health


# ── LangChain (8036) ───────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Status
GET {{langchain}}/langchain/status

### Create chain
POST {{langchain}}/langchain/chains
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "qa-chain",
  "description": "Simple Q&A chain",
  "chain_type": "simple",
  "template": "Answer the question: {question}"
}

### Run chain
POST {{langchain}}/langchain/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "chain_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "inputs": {"question": "What is Trancendos?"}
}


# ── LlamaIndex (8096) ──────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Status
GET {{llamaindex}}/llamaindex/status

### Create index
POST {{llamaindex}}/llamaindex/indexes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "platform-docs",
  "description": "Trancendos platform documentation"
}

### Ingest document
POST {{llamaindex}}/llamaindex/ingest
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "index_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "content": "Trancendos is a self-hosted zero-cost AI platform with 43 named entities.",
  "doc_id": "intro-001",
  "metadata": {"source": "CLAUDE.md"}
}

### Query index
POST {{llamaindex}}/llamaindex/query
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "index_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "query": "What is Trancendos?",
  "top_k": 3
}


# ── Haystack (8097) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Status
GET {{haystack}}/haystack/status

### Create pipeline
POST {{haystack}}/haystack/pipelines
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "rag-pipeline",
  "description": "RAG retrieval pipeline",
  "pipeline_type": "retrieval"
}

### Add document
POST {{haystack}}/haystack/documents
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pipeline_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "content": "The Spark is the MCP server and AI tool registry for Trancendos.",
  "doc_id": "spark-001",
  "metadata": {"entity": "The Spark"}
}

### Run pipeline
POST {{haystack}}/haystack/run
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "pipeline_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "query": "What is The Spark?",
  "top_k": 3
}


# ── DSPy (8098) ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────

### Status
GET {{dspy}}/dspy/status

### Create program
POST {{dspy}}/dspy/programs
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "name": "qa-program",
  "description": "Question answering",
  "signature": "question -> answer"
}

### Add example
POST {{dspy}}/dspy/examples
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "program_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "input_data": {"question": "What is DSPy?"},
  "expected_output": {"answer": "DSPy is a framework for programming language model pipelines."}
}

### Compile program
POST {{dspy}}/dspy/compile
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "program_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "optimizer": "BootstrapFewShot"
}

### Execute program
POST {{dspy}}/dspy/execute
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "program_id": "REPLACE_WITH_ID",
  "input_data": {"question": "What is Trancendos?"}
}
